{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"# Short Obligatory Prayer\n## To be recited once in twenty-four hours, at noon.\n\nO na God, na i pilere, kanire te beten di iterama di erienga. Na malia wen di iteiwa. Na niminin ta milekiwa, i niminin go milinwa. Na kalkan ta paina tekimua, i kal muru wen paitomua.\nGod ta ta milekimua, i teran wen milinwa. Talame Ugain ateral de erune i kenin erinwa. I ibal ta ta erionga milekinwa, i inin kaia mile paingal painwa.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","source":"bw18","version":"139b051a-042d-4201-bc98-449d9352943b","book_cats":{"af":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","order_in_cat":1},"am":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","order_in_cat":1},"ar":{"cat":"الصلاة   الصغيرة","order_in_cat":1},"az":{"cat":"Qısa Namaz","order_in_cat":1},"be":{"cat":"Кароткая абавязковая малітва","order_in_cat":1},"bg":{"cat":"Кратка задължителна молитва","order_in_cat":1},"ca":{"cat":"Oració obligatòria curta","order_in_cat":1},"cs":{"cat":"Krátká denní modlitba","order_in_cat":1},"da":{"cat":"Kort Obligatorisk Bøn","order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Das kurze Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"es":{"cat":"Oración obligatoria corta","order_in_cat":1},"fa":{"cat":"نماز صغیر","order_in_cat":1},"fi":{"cat":"Lyhyt velvollisuusrukous","order_in_cat":1},"fr":{"cat":"Prières prescrites","order_in_cat":1},"ha":{"cat":"Sallar Farilla Gajera","order_in_cat":1},"hi":{"cat":"मध्यम अनिवार्य प्रार्थना","order_in_cat":1},"hu":{"cat":"Rövid kötelező ima","order_in_cat":1},"is":{"cat":"Stutta skyldubænin","order_in_cat":1},"it":{"cat":"Preghiera Obbligatoria Breve","order_in_cat":1},"ja":{"cat":"短い必須の祈り","order_in_cat":1},"kl":{"cat":"Pinngitsoorani Qinnutissaq Naatsoq","order_in_cat":1},"km":{"cat":"Short Obligatory Prayer","order_in_cat":1},"kn":{"cat":"ಅನಿವಾರ್ಯ ಪ್ರಾರ್ಥನೆ","order_in_cat":1},"lb":{"cat":"Kuerzt Flichtgebiet","order_in_cat":1},"lt":{"cat":"Trumpa privalomoji malda","order_in_cat":1},"lv":{"cat":"Īsā obligātā lūgšana","